snippet.textDisplay:
My Dearest Future Wife,
With every beat of my heart, I yearn for you. Across time and distance, our souls intertwine. You, my love, hold the key to my existence. This song echoes our tale of love, uniting our destinies. Forever yours. . And lastly As I close my eyes, I envision the ethereal beauty that surrounds you. This melodic masterpiece effortlessly captures the essence of your radiance, evoking emotions that words fail to express. In its harmonies, I find the language of my love for you. Forever enchanted, Your Admirer.
Your future husband
